{"tid":1383962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有發夢既人 (長文慎入","createTime":"2019-07-29T20:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:58:26.000Z","uid":218530,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"858c518788cf3fc7ba5f710c2e24764334910543","tid":1383962,"uid":218530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:55:05.000Z","msg":"首先多謝每位有份岀黎發夢既手足<br />\n每個都為左同一件事一齊堅持<br />\n成件事好熱血<br />\n<br />\n作為其中一位FA<br />\n好多謝你地係前線打到七彩既時候對我地不離不棄<br />\n記得721個日有人話保住 fa 同 press<br />\n真係好感動<br />\n<br />\n但係入返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正題</span><br />\n有小部分既fa 幫手落雨開遮 搬鐵馬<br />\n唔係想屌你 作為其中一個fa我都想一齊搬<br />\n但係同時你都要知道<br />\n著得起件反光背心 <br />\n就要知道自己既立場係中立<br />\n同知道自己責任係咩<br />\n只要著住背心做左前線野<br />\n就好有可能會比位人入到<br />\n之後班狗就唔會再信fa 同press<br />\n<br />\n有咩事我地都係前面 <br />\n因為可以幫班手足頂到同拖時間比佢地撤<br />\n如果我地有事 下次就連我地都佢地唔到<br />\n依個時候無左一個就差好遠<br />\n唔好做傻事<br />\n<br />\n記住我地爭取緊既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a30fdfd3e77f0d0592fe97be2ebac42fbb07fbc7","tid":1383962,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:57:02.000Z","msg":"推，辛苦晒你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9af0090dcb9b056b8beecb8d915311cf8910d57","tid":1383962,"uid":218530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a30fdfd3e77f0d0592fe97be2ebac42fbb07fbc7","tid":1383962,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:57:02.000Z","msg":"推，辛苦晒你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:58:26.000Z","msg":"我都多謝你地岀黎發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0bb2a6c7a8de85769be0f1aed1568f5f07f478","tid":1383962,"uid":281159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:02:37.000Z","msg":"辛苦你地了 無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係痴線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382820</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"134475640a84ce80bc40ee84ba87e2016b929770","tid":1383962,"uid":238546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔好挽我啦 我多謝你地就真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰日冇夢見你班fa抬我走 我死撚咗喺上環喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df103c481a2b6b1483c4b5d5fdb2b95081ed171","tid":1383962,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:58:31.000Z","msg":"大家共同進退！<br />\n話說拾荒執到一大堆哮喘藥點算好？<br />\n我有派過比FA<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[窮學生] 我只需要你地管理好物！資！仲有上！前！線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d04e210f736e04f2160e05ea14bbf4afdd762849","tid":1383962,"uid":218530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df103c481a2b6b1483c4b5d5fdb2b95081ed171","tid":1383962,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:58:31.000Z","msg":"大家共同進退！<br />\n話說拾荒執到一大堆哮喘藥點算好？<br />\n我有派過比FA<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[窮學生] 我只需要你地管理好物！資！仲有上！前！線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:01:36.000Z","msg":"ching見到前線同背心就比啦 佢地好多都要用"},{"pid":"3e0c1b6d46e65b800bf9aacf21847d32eb1a68dc","tid":1383962,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04e210f736e04f2160e05ea14bbf4afdd762849","tid":1383962,